---
import VizPlaceholder from '../../VizPlaceholder.astro';
---

<section
  id="top"
  class="relative flex min-h-[calc(100svh-61px)] flex-col px-6"
>
  <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
    <h1
      class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-50 sm:text-7xl"
    >
      The Meta-Harness
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-neutral-400 sm:text-2xl">
      Elevating your harness for the new era of agentic work.
    </p>
    <a
      href="#what-is"
      class="mt-12 inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-neutral-800 px-6 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-300 transition-colors hover:border-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-50"
    >
      Enter
      <span aria-hidden="true">&darr;</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div
    class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1 pb-6 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-600"
  >
    <span>Scroll down</span>
    <span aria-hidden="true">&darr;</span>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="what-is" class="px-6 pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-50 sm:text-5xl"
      >
        Meta-harnesses elevate the primitive.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-300">
        A harness is a primitive. Claude Code, Codex, and OpenCode are excellent
        at one thing: turning a model into an agent that acts inside a repo.
        Your work, meanwhile, is moving up a level: the whole stack, many
        repositories, many sessions at once. Everyone hand-stitches workflows to
        bridge that gap, just like everyone built around React until the
        meta-frameworks arrived. <strong class="font-semibold text-neutral-50"
          >The meta-harness is that layer: batteries included for agentic
          work.</strong
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-5xl">
    <VizPlaceholder label="MetaHarnessLayers island" ratio="aspect-[16/10]" />
  </div>
</section>
